docs.text: Name Details DATA/ Contains .INT files. EXT/ Contains audio tracks for the game's Record Shop. IRX/ Contains IOP Relocatable eXecutable (IRX) library files. PSS/ Contains Sunny Funny's secret FMV. This is missing in the NTSC-J release. SND/ Contains all instrumental tracks for every stage in the game. VS/ Contains the opening and instrumental tracks for every Battle Mode stage. XTR/ Contains assets for every cutscene in the game. SYSTEM.CNF Contains disk autorun information. (serial number) The game binary.
